nodes.text: LEGO Star Wars Expanded Universe or LEGO Star Wars Legends is a subtheme of LEGO Star Wars sets based on elements from the Expanded Universe. So far, few sets have been released under the subtheme, with sets based on Star Wars: The Force Unleashed and Star Wars: The Old Republic making up the majority of the sets. Additional sets include the TIE/D Defender and the century tank.
